422
00:43:23,685 --> 00:43:25,020
And now,

423
00:43:26,605 --> 00:43:29,816
suddenly, this evening,
it makes perfect sense.

424
00:43:35,322 --> 00:43:37,157
Welcome, James.

425
00:43:40,785 --> 00:43:42,704
It's been a long time.

426
00:43:43,997 --> 00:43:46,333
