00:47:04,531 --> 00:47:07,242
It's one organization
coordinating multiple attacks.

446
00:47:07,325 --> 00:47:08,618
So, she was right.

447
00:47:08,701 --> 00:47:09,869
<i>Of course, she was.</i>

448
00:47:09,953 --> 00:47:11,955
- I ran that check.
- MAN: Who is it?

449
00:47:13,206 --> 00:47:16,501
Oh, my boss had his
credit card stolen.

450
00:47:16,543 --> 00:47:18,837
