451
00:47:18,878 --> 00:47:19,879
Don't be long.

452
00:47:19,963 --> 00:47:21,548
- Who was that?
- MONEYPENNY: <i>No one.</i>

453
00:47:21,798 --> 00:47:23,049
BOND: <i>No, it wasn't.</i>

454
00:47:23,091 --> 00:47:24,300
It's just a friend.

