489
00:51:43,768 --> 00:51:45,728
We will now vote
on the resolution.

490
00:51:46,229 --> 00:51:49,148
Ladies and gentlemen,
please cast your vote.

491
00:51:54,487 --> 00:51:56,489
The vote is eight
to one in favor.

492
00:51:56,906 --> 00:51:58,658
However, as you know,

493
00:51:58,699 --> 00:52:01,661
we cannot proceed
unless by unanimous vote.

494
00:52:02,161 --> 00:52:04,914
The Nine Eyes motion
is therefore not passed.

495
00:52:05,832 --> 00:52:06,999
Democracy.

496
00:52:07,083 --> 00:52:08,084
CHAIRMAN: Thank you,
ladies and gentlemen.

497
00:52:08,167 --> 00:52:09,752
- This evening's session is adjourned.
